      <sparkle:version>10.10</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>10.10</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed cross-device Claude web cookie sync so two Macs no longer overwrite each other's fresh session and silently log you out.</li>
          <li>Restore now picks the most recent cookies between local Keychain and the iCloud bundle instead of always trusting local.</li>
          <li>Expired cookies are filtered on save and restore, and SameSite is preserved across sync round-trips.</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
